snippet.title: Jiboner Golpo
snippet.description:
Jiboner Golpo is a channel where you can see real life Vlogs of me and my family and whatever happens around me. 

I upload videos everyday at 8 pm Bangladesh Time and I believe that my simple lifestyle will make a positive impact on everyone.

So if you are someone who understands Bangla, I am confident you will enjoy every second of your time spent on my channel.

If this sounds good, hit the Subscribe button and hop on the ride :)
